OL,3,C"I can't afford life": Council tax
OL,4,Crise piles pressure on cost of living
OL,6,FCouncil tax pays for local services
OL,7,Fsuch as schools, social care, the
OL,8,Fmaintenance of roads, bin collections,
OL,9,Fand many other essential services for
OL,10,Fthe local community.
OL,12,FBut campaingers warn the increases
OL,13,Fcome at a time when people are already
OL,14,Fstruggling with the cost of living.
OL,16,FTheresa Ruckley, from Barry, relies on
OL,17,Fa food bank for support and said:
OL,18,F"January was the most trying month of
OL,19,Fmy life."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
