PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1774598700
OL,3,C"I can't afford life": Council tax
OL,4,Crise piles pressure on cost of living
OL,6,FShe said its a "daily struggle" when
OL,7,Fdeciding to turn on the heating,
OL,8,Fbecause of the rise in gas and
OL,9,Felectricity bills.
OL,11,FTheresa is encouraging others to not
OL,12,Fbe ashamed to get support from food
OL,13,Fbanks as she has found them invaluable.
OL,15,FRachel Hassan helps run the Vale
OL,16,Ffoodbank in Barry and says they have
OL,17,Fseen an 18% increase in service users
OL,18,Fin the first three months of this year
OL,19,Fcompared to last year.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/14
