OL,3,C"I can't afford life": Council tax
OL,4,Crise piles pressure on cost of living
OL,6,FShe says the war in Iran and the 6.5%
OL,7,Fcouncil tax increase coming into
OL,8,Feffect in the Vale of Glamorgan will
OL,9,Flead to more people turning to them
OL,10,Ffor support.
OL,12,FIn a statement, Cllr Lis Burnett,
OL,13,FLeader of the Vale of Glamorgan
OL,14,FCouncil, said: "The Council conducted
OL,15,Fa wide-ranging consultation on budget
OL,16,Fproposals and this feedback helped
OL,17,Fshape decisions about council tax.
OL,26,@vD@POU
