OL,3,C"I can't afford life": Council tax
OL,4,Crise piles pressure on cost of living
OL,6,F"Residents told us where they wanted
OL,7,Fmoney to be spent and we have
OL,8,Fprioritised those areas by investing
OL,9,Fin schools, more council homes, social
OL,10,Fcare, roads and pavements.
OL,12,F"People in the Vale continue to pay
OL,13,Fless council tax than those living in
OL,14,F16 of the other 22 Welsh Local
OL,15,FAuthorities and the increase of 6.5
OL,16,Fper cent means people living in a
OL,17,Fproperty halfway along the banding
OL,18,Fscale in category D pay #2.07 more a
OL,19,Fweek.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/14
