OL,3,C"I can't afford life": Council tax
OL,4,Crise piles pressure on cost of living
OL,6,F"As well the areas already mentioned,
OL,7,Fmoney raised from council tax will
OL,8,Falso help pay for improved
OL,9,Fstreetlighting and public spaces,
OL,10,Fwhile one per cent has been ring-
OL,11,Ffenced for the Youth Service and rural
OL,12,Fpublic transport."
OL,14,FHow are council tax increases decided?
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@RO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/14
