OL,3,C"I can't afford life": Council tax
OL,4,Crise piles pressure on cost of living
OL,6,FThe political momentum to reform the
OL,7,Fcouncil tax funding model for Wales
OL,8,Fhas been growing.
OL,10,FIn a statement reacting to the average
OL,11,F4.9% increase in council tax, the
OL,12,FWelsh Conservatives said: "After 27
OL,13,Fyears of a Labour Government we have
OL,14,Fseen council tax increase and the cost
OL,15,Fof living in Wales is putting
OL,16,Fhouseholds under serious pressure.
OL,26,@tD@[OU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
