OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1774598700
OL,3,C"I can't afford life": Council tax
OL,4,Crise piles pressure on cost of living
OL,6,F"The Welsh Conservatives will put more
OL,7,Fmoney back in people's pockets by
OL,8,Fcapping council tax increases at 5%
OL,9,Fand require local referendums for
OL,10,Flarger rises."
OL,12,FPlaid Cymru said: "After 27 years of a
OL,13,FLabour Government we have seen council
OL,14,Ftax increase and the cost of living in
OL,15,FWales is putting households under
OL,16,Fserious pressure.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@NO]tD@SOU
