OL,3,C"I can't afford life": Council tax
OL,4,Crise piles pressure on cost of living
OL,6,F"The Welsh Conservatives will put more
OL,7,Fmoney back in people's pockets by
OL,8,Fcapping council tax increases at 5%
OL,9,Fand require local referendums for
OL,10,Flarger rises."
OL,12,FA Welsh Labour spokesperson said:
OL,13,F"Welsh Labour has made our council tax
OL,14,Fsystem fairer. Wales is only part of
OL,15,Fthe UK to have revalued council tax
OL,16,Fand we've introduced a Council Tax
OL,17,FReduction Scheme so that around one in
OL,18,Ffive households receive support to pay
OL,19,Ftheir bills.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@NO]uD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/14
