OL,3,C"I can't afford life": Council tax
OL,4,Crise piles pressure on cost of living
OL,6,F"We will cap council tax rises to ease
OL,7,Fthe cost of living."
OL,9,FThe Welsh Government says: "We have
OL,10,Fprovided local authorities with #6.56
OL,11,Fbillion to spend on delivering key
OL,12,Fservices in 2026-27, an increase of
OL,13,F4.5%.
OL,15,F"The setting of local budgets, council
OL,16,Ftax and the level of reserves are
OL,17,Fmatters for the elected members in
OL,18,Feach council.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@TO]qD@\OUwD@AOU
