OL,3,C"I can't afford life": Council tax
OL,4,Crise piles pressure on cost of living
OL,6,F"The formula which distributes funding
OL,7,Fbetween authorities considers a range
OL,8,Fof factors, including population
OL,9,Fcohorts, deprivation and sparsity, and
OL,10,Fis agreed and reviewed with local
OL,11,Fgovernment annually."
